name: MEKA PIG
description:
MEKA PIG is a boar demon robot. Created by OBYØR Laboratory.

Injected with black magic technology. Kind of magic to help people become rich instantly, but in exchange they must sacrifice something.

People in Nusaverse who own this MEKA PIG can transformed into a boar demon robot for a period of time. After the transformation, the demon boar roams around the Nusaverse to steal your Tezos wallet.

MEKA PIG is small
MEKA PIG is invisible
MEKA PIG is black
MEKA PIG is scary

MEKA PIG IS A GLITCH!
